data.description: Come and see this beautifully updated 2 Bedroom home in one of the most desired planned unit communities in Redding. Everything about this home exudes peace and warmth from the beautiful floors to the immaculate master suite to the peaceful back patio. The shared community has incredible amenities including a gorgeous pool area, clubhouse, koi ponds, walking paths, creeks and great neighbors. All of this in an excellent location close to Redding's best shopping, restaurants and more. This beautifully updated home includes 2 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms upstairs with a half bath down stairs. The dining room seamlessly transitions to the living room creating a wonderful atmosphere for hosting friends around the gorgeous fireplace. Come checkout this home today!
